data.title: Supa-Star Tim Burns returns for Supanova Melbourne and Gold Coast in April, joining his Mad Max co-star Steve Bisley! Tim is best known...
data.meta_description:
supanovaexpo on March 14, 2024: "Supa-Star Tim Burns returns for Supanova Melbourne and Gold Coast in April, joining his Mad Max co-star Steve Bisley!

Tim is best known for his role as the crazed Johnny the Boy in the 1979 classic, Mad Max. Tim also featured in the television series, Patrol Boat, as "Chef" McKinnon, and appeared in The Dismissal, Cop Shop, Glenview High and more!

For more info on Tim, visit supa.fans/TBurns

#supanova #melbourne #melbnova #goldcoast #goldnova #supastar #madmax #johnnytheboy #timburns #convention".
